    {
      "id": "scene_109_world4_home",
      "worldId": "world4",
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker": "",
      "dialogue": "你回到家。\n\n空荡荡的房间。\n\n父母还在工作，你一个人。\n\n「也许...真的是梦吧。」",
      "background": "classroom",
      "characters": [],
      "nextSceneId": "scene_110_world4_dream"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_109_world4_walk",
      "worldId": "world4",
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker": "",
      "dialogue": "你在街上漫无目的地走着。\n\n路过学校后面的废弃图书馆时，你停下了脚步。\n\n那栋楼...在发光？",
      "background": "school_sunset",
      "characters": [],
      "nextSceneId": "scene_110_world4_glow"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_109_world4_library",
      "worldId": "world4",
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker": "",
      "dialogue": "你来到学校图书馆。\n\n在书架间穿行时，一本古老的书吸引了你的注意。\n\n书皮上刻着奇怪的符号...和梦中一样的符号。",
      "background": "library",
      "characters": [],
      "nextSceneId": "scene_110_world4_book"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_110_world4_dream",
      "worldId": "world4",
      "type": "choice",
      "speaker": "",
      "dialogue": "晚上，你躺在床上。那个梦再次浮现。你选择：",
      "background": "classroom",
      "characters": [],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_041_a",
          "text": "【记录】写下梦境",
