    {
      "id": "scene_111_world4_search",
      "worldId": "world4",
      "type": "narration",
      "speaker": "",
      "dialogue": "你在网上搜索。\n\n「裂隙」、「穿越者」、「创造者」...\n\n居然...找到了一些相关信息？",
